        "code": { "language": "markdown", "showLineNumbers": false },
        "content": "**Read totals, not rate peaks.** k6 runs 8 sequential bursts (~110s). Set range to **Last 15 minutes** and use the **Totals** bargauges — they should match k6 counters (e.g. ~77k requests/run). Rate panels show req/s per minute bucket; brief bursts smear and layers spike at different times.",
